Salaries

This app scrapes salary data from Hoopshype.com and combines them into one single table that is sortable and filterable.

Stats

per_game_stats <- NBAPerGameStatistics(season = 2017)

(filter <- per_game_stats %>% 
    group_by(Player, Pos) %>%
    filter(Tm == "TOT" | n()==1))
